{"tid":2249602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【廢過童軍】一名中國士兵懷疑迷路越過印度邊境被捕，印方將送回","createTime":"2020-10-19T12:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:15:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eddcd84deaba0e5523c750e3c4e65ecc2df6a5fb","tid":2249602,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555578-20201019.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555578-20201019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zm9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=eb624334\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555578-20201019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8762abd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555578-20201019.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印度軍方證實，一名中國士兵在中印有主權爭議的拉達克地區迷路，越過印度邊境，被印方拘捕，印方完成既定程序後，會將這名士兵送回中國。<br />\n<br />\n印度軍方發表聲明，表示這名解放軍士兵已獲得氧氣、食物、保暖衣物，以免受高海拔的惡劣條件影響。<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》總編緝胡錫進表示，經了解確實有一名中國軍人被印方扣留，很可能是迷路所致，中印正在溝通，印方的態度比較積極，雙方正朝著妥善解決事件的方向努力，又相信事件不會導致邊境地區新的緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不如去香港童軍, 考返個章啦！屌你老母！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hksoc.org/images/banner-contact.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksoc.org%2Fimages%2Fbanner-contact.jpg&h=79c31bbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b3cf5b05dec471ef43df318c6a112343dddf933","tid":2249602,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"370fa1347f1c5febb21364a16697234c69f5844e","tid":2249602,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/d